    <p>The CBOE Volatility Index (VIX) measures expected 30-day volatility on the S&amp;P 500. Known as the "fear gauge," it rises when investors buy protective puts. Here is where the VIX sits today relative to historical zones.</p>
    <div class="tool-card" style="text-align:center;">
